headline: Provi Welcomes Chief Product and Technology Officer to Drive Digital Growth and Innovation in Beverage Alcohol
summary: CHICAGO, June 23, 2025--Provi, the largest online B2B marketplace for the beverage alcohol industry, has named Qingqing Ouyang as its Chief Product and Technology Officer. Ouyang brings extensive leadership experience from high-growth technology companies and will lead Provi’s ongoing investment in digital innovation to strengthen connectivity across all three tiers of the beverage alcohol industry.
